GOVERNMENT OF INDIA(BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT(MNTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
Department of Cabinet Affairs(Mantrimandal Karya Vibhag)
New Delhi, 23 July, 1972._
Sravana, 1894.
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect
from the forenoon of July 23, 1972,
(1) Shri D.P. Dhar assumed the office of Minister
of Planning (Yojana Mantri) and
(ii) Shri T.A. Pal assumed the office of Minister of
Railways (Rail Mantri).
